import React from 'react'
import { Button, Card } from 'react-bootstrap'

function Note() {
  return (
    <> 
        <Card>
            <Card.Body>
                <Card.Title>{}</Card.Title>

                <Card.Text></Card.Text>
                <Button variant="danger">Excluir</Button>
            </Card.Body>
        </Card>
    
    </>
  )
}

export default Note
